{"tid":587994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家小心個所謂香港研究協會懷疑佩票","createTime":"2018-03-11T01:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T02:04:49.000Z","uid":43152,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"09b1f545904dad5aa61276c468cfbb69df794241","tid":587994,"uid":43152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:26:36.000Z","msg":"Sorry for 1999先，第一次開post<br />\n啱啱落樓投票，投完就出嚟見到有條友話做民調<br />\n一聽條友講野已經知佢常用本語言係蝗語，即刻渣流灘俾假資料。個啲問題大概想知你今次投邊個，之前投邊個，之後問你滿唔滿意中央9唔搭8。又無禮貌。雖然唔知佢攞我啲答案做咩柒，今次唔係黑就白，都無選擇，歸曬邊，完全無佩票意義。可能想睇幾多巴絲射落海，方便下次選舉。總之，大家小心唔好益支拿"},{"pid":"7a738ee109830c25d0add6b1eaa2bb62e2499b8b","tid":587994,"uid":43152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:28:48.000Z","msg":"補反個事後上網搵到個會嘅19野<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1039194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1039194&d=sCBQETI3%2ByH5B5KK9iu7CMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=eef585ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1039194&h=018190ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1039194</a>"},{"pid":"1cdb26a2e27c0667e4fc6e90b039aa51fcf9f6c8","tid":587994,"uid":29784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:30:41.000Z","msg":"單議席單票配咩鳩野票"},{"pid":"1052de869d6308c68c6acfc2fbeb5408ca945040","tid":587994,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:34:17.000Z","msg":"呢個會存在幾屆，背後咩組織好明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1138dd8469681c1d1a112f599a7b65b34005a965","tid":587994,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cdb26a2e27c0667e4fc6e90b039aa51fcf9f6c8","tid":587994,"uid":29784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:30:41.000Z","msg":"單議席單票配咩鳩野票"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T02:03:51.000Z","msg":"咪係，最後等結果咪知啲票嘅分佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1270e80d7a726